| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6550 — Recovery Inhibition (safepay)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9588df36-a9c4-5f26-bed5-82fd56f1ca6f"
